caption: The chicken wings here are the BEST IN THE WORLD!!!! They are so big and so tasty it's unreal!!! I had the Jamaican jerk flavor and it was absolutely incredible! I ordered 15 but could only eat about half! The wings are so sticky and crispy, it's absolutely divine. Very good prices too!

(Translated by Google) This restaurant took 2 names on the takeaway website that were not related to the name of the restaurant to deceive consumers! It's a Xinjiang restaurant and a fried pork restaurant! And the name Yeli Xiali is a registered trademark of Xinjiang Catering Company in China!  (Original) 这个餐厅在外卖网站上取了2个和店名不相干的名字 欺骗消费者！ 又是新疆餐厅 又是炒猪肉餐厅 ！并且耶里夏利这个名字在中国是正规注册商标的新疆餐饮公司！

(Translated by Google) Master Zhang's craftsmanship is unstable, sometimes delicious and sometimes not delicious. The main reason was that the meat had not been processed properly and had a bloody smell. After searching for a long time, I didn't find half a ginger. 🤷‍♀️🤷‍♂️  (Original) 张师傅手艺不稳，时而好吃时而不好吃。主要是肉没处理好，有血腥味儿，找了半天也没发现半颗姜。🤷‍♀️🤷‍♂️
